Name: Iso3166-1-2
Title: Iso 3166 Part 1: 2 Letter Codes
Descriptino: This value set defines the ISO 3166 Part 1 2-letter codes

Name: CancerStageVS
Title: Cancer Stage Group Value Set
Descriptino: The result of cancer staging, i.e., the stage or category of the cancer.

Name: CancerStagingMethodVS
Title: Cancer Staging Method Value Set
Descriptino: System or method used for staging cancers. The terms in this value set describe staging systems, not specific stages or descriptors used within those systems.

Name: CancerStagingTypeVS
Title: Cancer Staging Type Value Set
Descriptino: Identifying codes for the type of cancer staging performed. In terms of the SNOMED CT hierarchy, these codes represent observables.

Name: ICDO3Morphologie
Title: Morphologie Codes des ICD-O-3 CodeSystems.

Name: ObdsOpKomplikationVS
Title: oBDS Operation Komplikation Value Set

Name: TNMDistantMetastasesCategoryMaxVS
Title: TNM Distant Metastases Maximum Value Set
Descriptino: Values for TNM distant metastases category must be selected from this value set, which includes all codes from UICC and all codes from TNMDistantMetastasesCategoryVS.

Name: TNMDistantMetastasesCategoryVS
Title: TNM Distant Metastases Category Value Set
Descriptino: Result values for M category. This value set contains SNOMED-CT equivalents of UICC codes for the M category, according to TNM staging rules.

Name: TNMDistantMetastasesStagingTypeVS
Title: TNM Distant Metastases Staging Type Value Set
Descriptino: Identifying codes for the type of cancer staging performed, i.e., clinical, pathological, or other, for distant metastases (M) staging observation.

Name: TNMPrimaryTumorCategoryMaxVS
Title: TNM Primary Tumor Maximum Value Set
Descriptino: Values for TNM primary tumor category must be selected from this value set, which includes all codes from UICC and all codes from TNMPrimaryTumorCategoryVS.

Name: TNMPrimaryTumorCategoryVS
Title: TNM Primary Tumor Category Value Set
Descriptino: Result values for T category. This value set contains SNOMED-CT equivalents of UICC codes for the T category, according to TNM staging rules.

Name: TNMPrimaryTumorStagingTypeVS
Title: TNM Primary Tumor Staging Type Value Set
Descriptino: Identifying codes for the type of cancer staging performed, i.e., clinical, pathological, or other, for primary tumor (T) staging observation.

Name: TNMRegionalNodesCategoryMaxVS
Title: TNM Regional Nodes Maximum Value Set
Descriptino: Values for TNM regional nodes category must be selected from this value set, which includes all codes from UICC and all codes from TNMRegionalNodesCategoryVS.

Name: TNMRegionalNodesCategoryVS
Title: TNM Regional Nodes Category Value Set
Descriptino: Result values for N category. This value set contains SNOMED-CT equivalents of UICC codes for the N category, according to TNM staging rules.

Name: TNMRegionalNodesStagingTypeVS
Title: TNM Regional Nodes Staging Type Value Set
Descriptino: Identifying codes for the type of cancer staging performed, i.e., clinical, pathological, or other, for regional nodes (N) staging observation.

Name: TNMStageGroupMaxVS
Title: TNM Stage Group Maximum Value Set
Descriptino: Values for TNM stage group must be selected from this value set, which includes all codes from UICC and all codes from TNMStageGroupVS.

Name: TNMStageGroupStagingTypeVS
Title: TNM Stage Group Staging Type Value Set
Descriptino: Identifying codes for the type of cancer staging performed, i.e., clinical, pathological, or other, for the stage group observation.

Name: TNMStageGroupVS
Title: TNM Stage Group Value Set
Descriptino: Result values for cancer stage group using TNM staging. This value set contains SNOMED-CT equivalents of UICC codes for Stage Group, according to TNM staging rules.

Name: TNMStagingMethodVS
Title: TNM Staging Method Value Set
Descriptino: Method used for TNM staging, e.g., UICC 6th, 7th, or 8th edition.

Name: ECOGPerformanceStatusVS
Title: ECOG
